title: Bhairavakona
subTitle: After committing a robbery, Basava and his companion, John, run into Agraharam Geetha, a stranger, and the trio end up in Bhairavakona, a village shrouded in mystery.

title: Welcome to New York
subTitle: A recovery agent and a designer become part of a big Bollywood event in New York, where chaos ensues, changing their lives forever.

title: Game Paisa Ladki
subTitle: Struggling with the loss of her loved ones, Nazuk becomes entangled with a gangster, planning to extort him and his associates for a reward of 10 crore rupees, setting the stage for a dangerous game.

title: Mission Majnu
subTitle: An undercover Indian spy takes on a deadly mission to expose a covert nuclear weapons program in the heart of Pakistan that could destroy the free world.

title: The Reunion
subTitle: Long after high school, Ricky has embraced a spiritual lifestyle. But when his childhood nemesis, Travis, is at their reunion, he sets off on a nightmarish journey of confrontation.

title: Acharya
subTitle: On behalf of an idyllic temple town, Acharya takes up the cudgels against a tyrant whose greedy sights are set on the local natural resources.

title: Chandu Champion
subTitle: An extraordinary man confronts relentless challenges with unwavering determination. His spirit and resilience propel him through adversity, ultimately forging a path to historic achievement.

title: Naach Lucky Naach
subTitle: Ten-year-old Lakshmi dreams of winning a national-level dance competition, but she hesitates to participate when her single mother, Nandini, detests music and dance.

title: Maine Pyar Kiya
subTitle: Prem and Suman fall in love with each other, only to be torn apart by family differences. However, Suman's father is willing to give Prem one last chance where he must prove himself worthy of Suman.

title: Himmatwar
subTitle: The son of a wealthy man leaves his family post a misunderstanding. Later, when he saves a police officer from an evil man, this results in him earning the latter's wrath.

title: Gadar: Ek Prem Katha
subTitle: A Sikh trucker and an aristocratic Muslim woman fall in love against the backdrop of the 1947 partition.

title: Crocodile Island
subTitle: The stranded passengers must fight against man-eating crocodiles after their plane makes an emergency landing on a remote island.

title: Crocodile Island
subTitle: The stranded passengers must fight against man-eating crocodiles after their plane makes an emergency landing on a remote island.

title: Om Jai Jagadish
subTitle: Divided by ideologies, yet bound by love, three brothers end up going their separate ways. Fate offers them another chance to be together when their family home is on the brink of foreclosure.

title: Kisko Tha Pata
subTitle: Shreya calls off her wedding with her boyfriend Devansh after a stranger predicts tragedy in their relationship. Later, she marries Dhairya and decides to start her life, but Devansh returns.

title: Uncaged
subTitle: A sleepwalking teen attaches a camera to himself at night. Later, he finds out a dark secret about his family from the footage.

title: Chennai vs China
subTitle: Aravind is a descendant of a martial arts expert, Bodhidharma. He must revive the fighting skills to stop Dong Lee, who comes to India to wage a biological war.

title: Main Prem Ki Diwani Hoon
subTitle: Sanjana falls in love with Prem Kishen after mistaking him for his boss, Prem Kumar, whom she is actually supposed to marry. But, the relationship is threatened when Prem Kishen reveals the truth.

title: Aitraaz
subTitle: When a company chairman's trophy wife stirs up a storm in a happily married employee's life, the tumultuous winds drag all of them into an intense courtroom showdown.

title: Chakra Ka Rakshak
subTitle: A police officer and soldier team up and decide to end the cybercriminals that pose a threat to the safety of people on the Internet.

title: Uri: The Surgical Strike
subTitle: Major Vihaan Singh Shergill of the Indian Army leads a covert operation against a group of militants who attacked a base in Uri, Kashmir, in 2016 and killed many soldiers.

title: Radhe: Your Most Wanted Bhai
subTitle: Radhe, a daredevil encounter specialist of the Mumbai Police force, vows to knock down the crime syndicate led by an evil drug lord.

title: Tera Jadoo Chal Gayaa
subTitle: To save Pooja's job, her friend lies to their boss, claiming that Pooja is engaged to Kabir, an artist. But this harmless lie spirals into a major misunderstanding between Pooja and Raj, the man she truly loves.

title: Bhoot Returns
subTitle: Tarun and Namrata move into a luxurious bungalow with Taman and Nimmi, their son and daughter respectively. However, strange occurrences start taking place and they must escape in order to survive.

title: Gully Boy
subTitle: The life of an underdog rapper from Dharavi who struggles to express his views on social issues through rapping, changes completely after he bumps into Shrikant alias MC Sher.

title: Bhootna
subTitle: Chang'an City is in an uproar over the appearance of a demon cat. A Chinese poet and a Japanese monk team up to pursue the creature after people experience a string of strange events.

title: Policegiri
subTitle: DCP Rudra operates in a city with rampant crime and corruption, courtesy Nagori Subramaniam. However, he decides to stand against him and destroy Nagori once and for all.

title: Ek Vivah Aisa Bhi
subTitle: A tragedy compels Chandni to put off her marriage and singing career. As she takes on new responsibilities, Prem holds their love in his heart for years, and waits for the day when she can come back to him.

title: Real Tevar
subTitle: Harsha is the idealistic scion of a self-made multimillionaire, Ravikanth. After a chance meeting with Charuseela leads him to a remote village, Harsha wishes to develop it with her help.

title: I
subTitle: A bodybuilder and successful model plans revenge after his enemies inject him with a substance that deforms his body.

title: Kaatera
subTitle: Kaatera, a blacksmith from a village named Bheemanahalli, goes through numerous threats so that a reforms act gets implemented which gives freedom to the farmers from feudal landlords.

title: Koogle Kuttappa
subTitle: A conservative villager hates the idea of his son relocating to Russia for a job. However, when his son brings a robot to care for him, he develops an unlikely bond with the machine.
